3. **Operator Chaining**: The `|` operator chains the SELECT and JOIN operations together, following the pattern shown in the reference materials.

4. **SQL Generation**: `sqlgen::sqlite::to_sql(query)` converts the constructed query object into an actual SQL string.

The generated SQL would be similar to:
```sql
SELECT u.name, p.title FROM User AS u LEFT JOIN Post AS p ON u.id = p.user_id
